CONNERS MARINE CO., Inc., Appellant, v. UNITED STATES GYPSUM CO., Appellee. No. 105. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Dec. 11, 1939. John E. Purdy, of New York City, for appellant. F. Herbert Prem, of New York City, for appellee.

Before L. HAND, CHASE, and PATTERSON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed on authority of Standard etc. Works v. Travelers Ins. Co., 4 Cir., 107 F.2d 373.
